{"article_id":"1ZBReCgHDERR8u4u","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congress Congress may stiff Trump on wall funding","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"Republicans are afraid of losing a government shutdown showdown .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Congressional Republicans might deliver some more bad news for President Donald Trump , fresh off their embarrassing failure","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to scrap Obamacare :","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"No new money is coming","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to build his wall .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Trump hoped to jump-start construction of a massive wall on the U.S.-Mexico border with money in a must-pass government funding bill .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"But Democratic leaders are vowing to block any legislation","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"that includes a single penny for the wall .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"With the GOP consumed by its own divisions ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"the White House and Hill Republicans will have to rely on Democratic votes","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"to avoid a government shutdown next month","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"in what would be another disaster for Trump ' s fledgling presidency .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"Republican leaders ,","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"wary of this ,","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"are considering a plan","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"that would not directly tie the border wall money to the April 28 government funding deadline .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"Some Republican insiders worry","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"that the president can not afford another major legislative setback","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"- and they believe","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"a shutdown showdown would result in just that .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"While no decision has been made by GOP leadership ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Republican lawmakers may decide to decouple the two","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to avoid a confrontation with Democrats .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"If they do ,","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"the chances","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"of getting Trump ' s wall funding passed this spring","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"become slim .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" It remains to be seen , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"said Senate Majority Whip John Cornyn","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"( R-Texas )","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"in an interview .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" What I would like to see is a plan","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"for how the money would be spent and a good faith discussion","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"about what border security is really composed of .","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"We haven ' t had that . \"","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Asked about the prospects for a lapse in government funding ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Cornyn was definitive :","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" There ' s not going to be a shutdown . \"","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"The White House made an initial request earlier this month for $ 1.4 billion in border wall funding as part of a package","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"that boosts defense spending by $ 30 billion ,","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"with the thought","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"that it would hitch a ride to the broader government funding bill due next month .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"Republicans expect","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"the final price tag for the wall could be more than $ 20 billion .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"The problem is that polls show","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"the border wall is not all that popular ,","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"particularly if the United States is paying for it ,","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"and it does not unify congressional Republicans in the way","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"Supreme Court nominee Neil Gorsuch or even the basic goal","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"of repealing Obamacare","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"have done .","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"That makes it a harder sell to the rank-and-file GOP","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"- especially if pressing it means playing a government shutdown blame game with Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"\" The border wall is probably not a smart investment , \"","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"said Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"( R-S.C. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"who proposes","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"funding the wall as part a package","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"legalizing some young undocumented immigrants","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"and beefing up enforcement .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"Several sources said","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"it is unclear whether Trump wants to take the fight to Democrats over the wall","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"or avoid a shutdown battle .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"His Office of Management and Budget Director Mick Mulvaney in recent weeks has suggested","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"the administration will focus more on the wall in the future , perhaps as late as fiscal 2019 .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"The White House didn ' t respond to a request for comment .","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"But building the wall was Trump ' s signature campaign promise .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Pushing off funding for it now would leave Trump with another unchecked campaign pledge at a time","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the White House is thirsty for a victory after its Obamacare debacle .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"Some defense hawks , like Graham , are concerned","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"that the border wall fight could complicate an effort","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"to get extra spending for the military .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"\" Democrats ,","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"I think ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"are in a spot","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"where they ' re open-minded to military spending","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"as long as it doesn ' t come at the expense of \" domestic spending ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Graham said .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"\" Here ' s what I ' d tell my colleagues in the House :","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"If you don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"the Defense Department is an emergency situation ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"you ' ve just stopped listening . \"","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"Of course , some in the GOP are itching for a border battle .","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"A senior Republican source suggested","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Trump could conceivably win a shutdown fight","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"if he went to the mat","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"to defend it :","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"\" This is his signature issue .","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"I can not imagine a scenario","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"where the Trump administration loses on the border wall funding .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"If I were them ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"I ' d dare the Democrats to shut down the government over this . \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Another senior House Republican source disagreed completely :","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"`` The Trump administration ca n't have another disaster on its hands .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"right now","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"they have to show some level of competence","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"and that they can govern . ''","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"Republicans began the year thinking","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"that they could get moderate Democrats and perhaps even Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"( D-N.Y. )","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"to fund construction of a wall","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that some Democrats have supported in the past .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"But Schumer has warned McConnell","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"that his party will not support any \" riders \" in the funding bill","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"intended to jam Democrats with conservative policies .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"\" The wall is a poison-pill rider , \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Schumer said in an interview .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"\" They ' ll do it at their peril . \"","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"Other than the issue of the wall , the spending process on Capitol Hill is proceeding apace .","depth":4},{"id":111,"text":"Republicans and Democrats are working diligently together on a measure","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"to fund the government through September","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that can appeal to the center of each party ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"according to lawmakers and aides .","depth":6},{"id":115,"text":"But adding the wall into the mix would create a toxic political environment .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"\" That ' s a bigger problem , \"","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"said a Republican senator familiar with the emerging spending bills .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Including wall funding in the must-pass government funding bill \" would be hard . \"","depth":6},{"id":119,"text":"While the chamber operates on majority rule","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"and could conceivably write red-meat appropriations bills","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"that include wall funding ,","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"GOP leaders expect a significant number of conservatives to defect on any government funding bill ,","depth":6},{"id":123,"text":"as they have in the past .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"And","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"after the hard-line House Freedom Caucus brought down the Obamacare replacement bill last week ,","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"GOP insiders worry","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"they can ' t depend on them","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"to help get major legislation across the finish line .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"The conservative caucus discussed giving Trump `` greater flexibility '' on spending bills during a closed-door Monday night meeting ,","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"according to Freedom Caucus Chairman Mark Meadows","depth":7},{"id":131,"text":"- so long as it includes funding for Trump 's wall .","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"Sign up here for Huddle","depth":4},{"id":133,"text":"A daily play-by-play of congressional news in your inbox .","depth":4},{"id":134,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":135,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":136,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":138,"text":"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA","depth":5},{"id":139,"text":"and the Google Privacy Policy and Terms of Service apply .","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"`` We understand","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"that we have a very narrow margin of victory...","depth":6},{"id":142,"text":"and we understand","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"it may require us to take more difficult votes","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"than we have in the previous Congress , ''","depth":7},{"id":145,"text":"the North Carolina Republican told reporters .","depth":4},{"id":146,"text":"One option for the House is to pass the government funding bill and the border and defense package in a way","depth":6},{"id":147,"text":"that allows the Senate to easily separate the two measures later .","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"Republicans could pass a bipartisan bill","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"keeping the government open","depth":8},{"id":150,"text":"and then attach a second GOP bill with wall funding .","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"That would let the Senate strip the wall provision from the must-pass bill","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"to avert a government shutdown ,","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"and the House would be forced to swallow what the Senate can pass .","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"If Trump insists ,","depth":7},{"id":155,"text":"House GOP leaders could include the wall money directly in the government funding bill","depth":7},{"id":156,"text":"- but they could lose only 22 Republicans","depth":7},{"id":157,"text":"if they receive no Democratic support .","depth":7},{"id":158,"text":"Even if the House manages to pass a spending measure","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"that includes funding for the wall ,","depth":8},{"id":160,"text":"Republicans will need at least eight Senate Democrats to break a filibuster","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"to fund the government ,","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"something","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"Schumer says","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"isn ' t happening","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"if border wall money is included .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":331,"left":297,"right":330,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":297,"left":275,"right":296,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":204,"right":274,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":167,"right":203,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":167,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":185,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":185,"left":170,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":168,"right":169,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":168,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":169,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":172,"right":183,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":172,"left":6,"right":171,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":171,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":175,"right":182,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":9,"right":174,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":174,"left":10,"right":173,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":178,"right":181,"relation":"advers